options.text: Have you any quests for me?

bf7e2bfb-b0bf-4123-9528-9ff68890341a.title: Duke Horacio
bf7e2bfb-b0bf-4123-9528-9ff68890341a.text:
I've heard that the blacksmiths are prosperous amongst
the peasantry. Maybe you could try your hand at
that?

727da863-2ff6-46b5-959e-44c47e40fed4.title: <player>
727da863-2ff6-46b5-959e-44c47e40fed4.text: Have you any quests for me?

8a9af6fe-821b-46e2-ba15-c86dc6915f8e.title: Duke Horacio
8a9af6fe-821b-46e2-ba15-c86dc6915f8e.text:
Well, it's not really a quest but I recently discovered
this strange talisman.

682f0b20-1f76-4862-bef3-a541ac0fe130.title: Duke Horacio
682f0b20-1f76-4862-bef3-a541ac0fe130.text:
It seems to be mystical and I have never seen anything
like it before. Would you take it to the head wizard at

8c0f226a-f379-4576-9962-e7e1b551a6b3.title: Duke Horacio
8c0f226a-f379-4576-9962-e7e1b551a6b3.text:
the Wizards' Tower for me? It's just south-west of here
and should not take you very long at all. I would be
awfully grateful.

c51648e6-34ed-48b4-94be-799ecc09b4d9.title: Duke Horacio
c51648e6-34ed-48b4-94be-799ecc09b4d9.text:
Thank you very much, stranger. I am sure the head
wizard will reward you for such an interesting find.

6d0309cf-902c-4f39-a632-f17d8f276e2f.title: Duke Horacio
6d0309cf-902c-4f39-a632-f17d8f276e2f.text:
As you wish, stranger, although I have this strange
feeling that it is important. Unfortunately, I cannot
leave my castle unattended.

options.text: Have you any quests for me?

25445a6a-f871-4a3f-9067-24399eebc25b.text:
I've heard that the blacksmiths are prosperous amongst
the peasantry. Maybe you could try your hand at
that?

3fafc08d-fb0e-4696-8c0b-b605481e2c5e.title: <player>
3fafc08d-fb0e-4696-8c0b-b605481e2c5e.text: Have you any quests for me?

d60f64d0-cdc6-499e-8366-c861c0715342.title: Duke Horacio
d60f64d0-cdc6-499e-8366-c861c0715342.text:
The only task remotely approaching a quest is the
delivery of that talisman I gave you to the head wizard
of the Wizards' Tower,

97d7b4ca-cd3a-4021-9036-58a7d538f2e3.title: Duke Horacio
97d7b4ca-cd3a-4021-9036-58a7d538f2e3.text:
south-west of here. I suggest you deliver it to him as
soon as possible. I have the oddest feeling that it is
important...

options.text: Have you any quests for me?

ca36a4a8-135a-4ddc-a368-29de001aa00f.text:
I've heard that the blacksmiths are prosperous amongst
the peasantry. Maybe you could try your hand at
that?

99f63a17-78c9-4a7d-bd89-f5dc10c1db8e.title: <player>
99f63a17-78c9-4a7d-bd89-f5dc10c1db8e.text: Have you any quests for me?

261552ea-3db3-4bc5-8ee3-e7a3c2835ed8.title: Duke Horacio
261552ea-3db3-4bc5-8ee3-e7a3c2835ed8.text: No, all is well for me.
